Name: Sicilian Salad
Description: The Sicilian Salad is a refreshing dish featuring crisp lettuce, juicy tomatoes, cucumbers, red onions, olives, mozzarella, capers, and optional anchovies, all tossed in a flavorful vinaigrette dressing.

Name: Bagnet
Description: Bagnet is prepared by boiling pork belly with aromatics until tender, then air-drying or refrigerating it to remove excess moisture. The pork belly is then deep-fried until golden brown and crispy. Ingredients typically include pork belly, garlic, bay leaves, peppercorns, and salt. It is often served with garlic rice, tomatoes, and a dipping sauce made from vinegar, soy sauce, and chili peppers.

Name: Vizcayas Pride Chickeneenee
Description: Combining potato chips and fried chicken into one dish creates a delightful crunchy and savory experience. In this dish, thinly sliced potato chips are used as a crispy coating for the fried chicken pieces, adding an extra layer of texture and flavor. The chicken is first seasoned with salt, pepper, and spices, then coated in a batter or flour mixture. Next, it's coated with the crushed potato chips before being deep-fried until golden brown and crispy.

Name: Peppered Fish with Grilled vegetable
Description: Peppered fish with grilled vegetables combines marinated fish and a variety of fresh veggies, grilled to perfection. The fish is seasoned with spices and crushed peppercorns for a spicy taste, while the vegetables are sliced and grilled until tender and charred. Together, they create a flavorful and colorful dish that celebrates the essence of grilled cuisine.

Name: Mushroom and Tofu
Description: Mushroom and tofu dish features a delightful combination of savory mushrooms and tofu cooked in a flavorful sauce. The mushrooms are sauted until golden brown, while the tofu is gently cooked to absorb the rich flavors of the sauce. This dish is both hearty and nutritious, offering a satisfying meal for vegetarians and vegans alike.

Name: Grilled Chicken Kebab with Curry
Description: Grilled chicken kebab with curry is a tantalizing fusion dish that combines the succulence of grilled chicken with the aromatic flavors of curry spices. Tender chunks of marinated chicken are skewered and grilled to perfection, then generously coated in a fragrant curry sauce. The result is a dish bursting with bold flavors and irresistible aromas, making it a favorite among enthusiasts of both grilled meats and exotic spices.

Name: Pork Steak
Description: Pork steak is a classic dish featuring tender cuts of pork loin or shoulder, seasoned and seared to perfection. Often marinated in a savory blend of herbs, spices, and sauces, the pork steak is then grilled or pan-fried until golden brown and juicy. Served hot off the grill or pan, pork steak delights with its rich flavor and succulent texture, making it a beloved choice for hearty meals and BBQ gatherings alike.
